@node "whatisit" "What is it?"

  What is  it  ?

  Kick is softkicker for Amiga 1200 with Blizzard turboboard. Unlike
  other kickers it features:

    - sophisticated graphical interface
    - fast and small (only 900 Bytes big) CLI kicker tool written in assembly
    - supports Kickstarts packed with XPK
    - recognizes different kickstarts of same version
    - works with both 256k and 512k kickstarts (1.0 - ...)
    - directory buffering for fast access (normally checking every kickstart is slow)
    - no system degrading features (like QUICKBOOT etc.)
    - totaly localized
    - comes with BootPic-like tool for showing configuration on startup
    - CKick tool is Kickstart 1.x compatible

@endnode
